Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveComrade Amos Ufuoma Asigri just got a wife—the second one at that.  And it could have been nothing new but for his peculiarity.
Asigiri is not handicapped I any way, but he’s vertically challenged, ad his wives are twice his height.
The latest bride comes from Isoko South Local Government Area of Delta state
Amos and Hope Ogheneuzuazor Ogbokor tied the knot on Saturday, April 30, at Uyoyou community in Ada-Irri.
He married to his first wife, princess Edith in 2018.
